---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#111] font-display">About</h1>

  <p class="mb-4">I'm a software engineer at Mews building production systems that actually hold up.</p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#222] font-display">Background</h2>

  <p class="mb-4">Started in software development, moved into building production systems when I saw how much potential there was to automate and improve workflows. Now my main focus is the gap between "it works locally" and "it runs reliably in production."</p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#222] font-display">What I Do</h2>

  <p class="mb-4">Building, deploying, and maintaining production systems. Writing code that doesn't make the next person curse my name.</p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#222] font-display">Connect</h2>

  <p><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/toni-esteso" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">LinkedIn</a></p>
</BaseLayout>